<b>Subject:</b> Why This game will not change,(Root,DoT,and Lootin)<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I will make this short and SWEET. Understand that The classel are all hunted, not just tanks by Wiz, Though I must keep some info to myself, I have found that many of my char have STR and WEEK to diff classes/races/combat styles, Most do see this, but some still dont agree, I can hunt and kill a wiz just as fast as he can me, If you dont feel safe running around as a tank with wiz everywhere that you cant see, group with an wiz,ench and so on, You will not be hunedt if that is the case, Trust me...Tanks start off as the soloing class, wizs kinda, ench not at all, This is to lvl out the game, You will not lose by grouping, but you need to make some friends, Good Luck, Good Hunting...

</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
